Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.80,0:01:19.02,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}運命の{\fscx75}Countdown
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:18.04,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夜风也茫然不解的旋律正在吹响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.50,0:00:22.54,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这既不是笑谈也不是游戏 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:30.16,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他人皆是对手 混沌的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.48,0:00:34.64,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}躲猫猫 如此危险的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.06,0:00:38.50,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嘀嗒嘀嗒 摩天楼上时钟作响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.50,0:00:41.54,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}悄然隐匿的 我心如陷阱与炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.86,0:00:46.84,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊啊啊 脱离成群的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.06,0:00:47.88,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}幸存者会是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:50.10,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}胜负仅此一回
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:53.20,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}此刻 点燃烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.64,0:01:00.66,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一步步地逼近 我所追求的更多赐予
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.34,0:01:04.64,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在被他人盗走前 你看 爱在燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.64,0:01:06.90,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感触到了热气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.14,0:01:12.08,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火辣辣的 刺激的浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.02,0:01:12.08,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1890, 180)\blur3\fs30}去感受它 去感受它 去感受它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:16.22,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}导火线的行踪就承载于风吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.80,0:01:19.02,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}命运的倒计时
